- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper presents a systematic construction method for elimination sets, which can be seen as an algorithmic approach. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper mentions Thom codes, which are used in the study of singularities in dynamical systems.
